{"tid":784810,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖開季]駱文捷 衛詩雅 蘇麗珊 胡琳 林映蔚 菊梓喬 #18-19 LIHKG香港乙組女神聯賽第一輪投選專區","createTime":"2018-08-18T16:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T15:12:39.000Z","uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"157f59603142ba9e462c19d56e7d4c31623db57b","tid":784810,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T16:29:30.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n由首場12:30am開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n<br />\n陳華鑫 : 何依婷<br />\n鄭宇澄 : 林穎彤<br />\n胡琳 : 何超蓮<br />\n何雁詩 : 駱文捷<br />\n鄺潔楹 : 林凱恩<br />\n龔嘉欣 : 蘇麗珊<br />\n周慧敏 : 勞嘉怡<br />\n菊梓喬 : 衛詩雅<br />\n車泳希 : 林映蔚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ffg4vwe7.png&d=Xsdeskq8uFyFfZ5uXwKFkBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=698e524e\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png</a><br />\n有關主場指定額外得分情況,請參閱主場額外分數增幅表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28af4ffe626ef72058139f830817bc24996009c6","tid":784810,"uid":92376,"like":63,"dislike":143,"score":-80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T16:30:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-19 LIHKG香港乙組女神聯賽第一輪</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-8-19 12:30am-10:30pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ZD7Krty.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZD7Krty.png&h=1f85aee8&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/y5Hc5zh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fy5Hc5zh.png&h=a7d6d003&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">陳華鑫vs何依婷</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"d3f188095649aa75325b9ecd6386faf77c851c9e","tid":784810,"uid":92376,"like":81,"dislike":155,"score":-74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T16:32:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-8-19 12:32am-10:32pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/bzPCRc8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FbzPCRc8.png&h=fe579f2c&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/yjGCn1b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FyjGCn1b.png&h=f1d7de4c&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">鄭宇澄vs林穎彤</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"dbaabc6db8eb0a97fc05d12e826d50cd9e917492","tid":784810,"uid":92376,"like":59,"dislike":170,"score":-111,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T16:34:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-8-19 12:34am-10:34pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/jvo6Orj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=